                         Namespace for Public Identifiers", RFC 3151,
                         August 2001.

   [RFC3553]             Mealling, M., Masinter, L., Hardie, T. and G.
                         Klyne, "An IETF URN Sub-namespace for
                         Registered Protocol Parameters", BCP 73, RFC
                         3553, June 2003.

